text: CS Măgura Cisnădie is a professional women's handball club in Cisnădie, Sibiu County, Romania, that competes in the Liga Naţională. ==Honours== ===Domestic competitions=== Liga Națională (National League of Romania) *15px Third place: 2017–18 ==Team== ===Current squad=== ;Goalkeepers: * Elena Voicu * Alexandra Prodan * Denisa Tudor ;Wingers ;LW * Dijana Radojević * Bianca Marin ;RW * Mădălina Predoi * Daniela Necula ;Line players * Dana Abed Kader * Timea Tătar ;Back players ;LB * Valentina Panici * Sylwia Lisewska ;CB * Andreea Ianăși * Valentina Blažević ;RB * Aleksandra Zych * Elena Gjeorgjievska ==Notable former players== * Ada Moldovan * Raluca Băcăoanu * Ana Maria Tănasie * Adriana Crăciun * Oana Apetrei * Nicoleta Tudor * Alina Horjea * Cătălina Cioaric * Mihaela Popescu * Deonise Fachinello * Larissa Araújo * Mariana Costa * Gabriela Moreschi * Jaqueline Anastácio * Jasna Boljević * Ivana Božović * Dijana Ujkić * Nataša Krnić ==External links== * Category:Liga Națională (women's handball) clubs Category:Handball clubs established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Romania Category:Sport in Sibiu County
